The paper presents a parallel algorithm for computing shortest paths in undirected graphs, which involves developing new tools and concepts such as low hop emulators and compressible preconditioners. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories related to distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), network optimization (cs.NE), computational geometry (cs.CG), and machine learning (cs.LG) which often deal with similar concepts and techniques.
